author: Ryan George Extra Plus!
description:
Ever dream of spending $4,000 a night to sleep in a concrete cube filled with driftwood sculptures and “live, laugh, love” energy? Welcome to the world of luxury Airbnbs - where every home has a record player no one uses, a bathtub in the middle of the living room, and a framed quote about how travel is the only thing that makes you richer.
